{"tid":400981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"強國B仔成個飛落地 副院長推嬰兒車當玩具","createTime":"2017-09-15T09:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T09:27:43.000Z","uid":75969,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e40a83dfbd17aedb82014ea505344ce84847678f","tid":400981,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:11:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170914/large/1505402600_54d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170914%2Flarge%2F1505402600_54d9.jpg&h=613223d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吉林延吉一間婦嬰護理服務中心，今年7月發生一宗初生嬰兒墮地事件，片段昨日曝光。該中心一名有20年經驗的副院長，將一名初生嬰兒推回育嬰室時，疑因用力不當，將嬰兒車推至翻倒，發出「嘭」的一聲，嬰兒應聲「飛」出車外，直接墮地。副院長和另一名工作人員隨即上前將嬰兒抱起，整個過程被中心的閉路電視拍下。<br />\n<br />\n據該中心工作人員表示，涉事副院長只是「小小的疏忽，人畢竟不是上帝，也有出事故的時候。她目前已不在該處工作。」嬰兒事後被送到當地醫院接受電腦掃瞄檢查，並未有發現任何問題。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>嬰兒家長，起初要求中心賠償61萬元（人民幣．下同），隨後又「減價」至30萬元，至近日又改口，目前雙方仍在協商中。</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170915/57211613\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170915%2F57211613&d=hYX%2BYVn9IVBUCSgwV1kXpv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=f6b289c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170915%2F57211613&h=68015c36\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170915/57211613</a><br />\n<br />\n個BB差少少就唔洗做中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8414cb2179ad1a37e81ba8c0ccde80354c2e071","tid":400981,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"啊斗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}